.Dd April 23, 2026
.Dt MAT_SETVERBOSE 3
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm Mat_SetVerbose
.Nd Sets the library verbose and silent logging levels.
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Fd #include <matio.h>
.Ft int
.Fo Mat_SetVerbose
.Fa "int verb"
.Fa "int s"
.Fc
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Fn Mat_SetVerbose
function stores the library verbose level
.Fa verb
and silent flag
.Fa s .
These values control message emission by
.Fn Mat_VerbMessage
and whether non-error messages are suppressed entirely.
.Sh RETURN VALUES
The function returns 0.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr Mat_SetDebug 3 ,
.Xr Mat_VerbMessage 3 ,
.Xr Mat_Message 3